**/.DS_Store

# Generated by deploy — root-level symlink to AGENTS.md (source of truth).
/CLAUDE.md

# Machine-specific SSH config (real hostnames/IPs, usernames) — lives at
# $XDG_CONFIG_HOME/ssh/config.local in practice, outside this repo
# entirely, so this never actually matches anything; here only as a
# safety net in case it's ever created inside the repo by mistake.
ssh/config.local

# Scoped-down GH_TOKEN for .envrc — never commit a real token
.envrc.local

# Machine-private Claude Code files — internal/work platform tooling that
# must never reach this public repo. Anything under platform/private/ is
# ignored by default, so a new private file is safe the moment it's created:
# no per-file gitignore edit to forget, and no internal platform name spelled
# out in this public file. The whole claude/rules/ tree deploys as one symlink
# and Claude Code discovers .md files recursively, so private/ still loads into
# $CLAUDE_CONFIG_DIR/rules. A fresh clone simply lacks the dir's contents.
# See claude/README.md § Private files.
claude/rules/platform/private/
